<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        font-family: arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 12pt;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">
    <p>Preview the <%= link_to 'new PQs', controller: 'early_bird_dashboard', action: 'index', token: @template_params[:token], entity: @template_params[:entity], :host => root_url %> for the <strong><%= Date.today.strftime "%d/%m/%Y" %></strong>. This link will only be active today.</p>
    <p>These PQs have not yet been allocated by the Ministry of Justice, Parliamentary Branch.</p>
    <p>Please <a href="mailto:<%= Settings.mail_reply_to %>">contact the PQ team</a> if any of these questions are for you or for your team.</p>
    <p>You have signed up to receive these daily emails. To unsubscribe, <a href="mailto:<%= Settings.mail_reply_to %>">contact the PQ Team</a>.</p>
    <p>This is a new service - your <a href="mailto:PQFeedback@digital.justice.gov.uk?Subject=PQ%20Feedback">feedback</a> will help us improve it.</p>
    <%= render 'shared/mailer/email_signature' %>
  </body>
</html>
